  P: Goa2 chham Jin5-ai3-a3 toa3 hia chio-hou i long2 be7 ho2-se3, u7 kou-chiaN5 i chiah8 chit8-oaN2 toa7-beh8-moai5, i2-goa7 mng7 teng2 mng7 e7, long2 m7 in3, goan2 to chiaN5-bo5 hoat-tou7, tu2 siuN7 beh ka7 chhoa7 khi3 phai3-chhut-sou2 e5 si5, chit8-e5 chheng7 se-chong e5 sin-su7 mng7 goan2 si7 an2-choaN2, au7-lai5 i theh8 chit8-tiuN phian3-toaN hou7 goan2, kong2 i toa3 ti7 Tai5-pak, m7-chai kong2 in chhu3 ti7 sim2-mih8 iN7 e5 keh-piah. Kong2 i beh ka7 chhoa7 khi3, na7-u7 lang5 chhoe7 chiah po3 khi3 i hia, goa2 to siuN7 kong2 chit-keng m7 chiaN5 tiam3-a2 thai3-se3-keng leh, koh Jin5-ai3-a3 ia7 iau2 boe7 cho3-kheh. 
